Subject: Your FedEx Package Tracking Information

Dear [Recipient],

We are pleased to inform you that your package with tracking number #123456789 has been successfully processed and is on its way to you. 

Estimated delivery date: [Date]
Delivery address: [Address]
Shipping method: FedEx Ground

You can track your package in real-time using the following link: [Tracking link]

For any further assistance or inquiries, please do not hesitate to contact us at [FedEx customer service number].

Thank you for choosing FedEx for your shipping needs.

Sincerely,
FedEx Shipping Team
